## 🛠️ CLI Generators

### Generate Full Resource

```bash
swap g r Product --fields "Name:string Price:decimal InStock:bool:f"
```

Creates:
- `Domain/Entities/Product.cs`
- `Application/Services/ProductService.cs`
- `Application/Interfaces/IProductService.cs`
- `Infrastructure/Repositories/ProductRepository.cs`
- `Web/Controllers/ProductsController.cs`
- `Web/Views/Products/Index.cshtml`
- `Web/Views/Products/_ProductList.cshtml`
- `Web/Views/Products/_ProductForm.cshtml`
- `Web/Views/Products/_ProductItem.cshtml`
- Event chains in `Web/Events/SwapEventChains.cs`

### Generate Model Only

```bash
swap g m Category --fields "Name:string Slug:string"
```

Creates:
- `Domain/Entities/Category.cs`

### Generate Controller Only

```bash
swap g c Orders --fields "OrderNumber:string Total:decimal"
```

Creates:
- `Web/Controllers/OrdersController.cs`
- Views (Index, _List, _Form, _Item)

**Field syntax:**
- `Name:string` — Required string
- `Description:string?` — Nullable string
- `Price:decimal` — Required decimal
- `InStock:bool:f` — Boolean with `false` default
- `Quantity:int` — Required integer

