## 🚨 Troubleshooting

### CSS not updating?

```bash
cd src/Web
Remove-Item wwwroot/css/app.css
npm run build:css
```

### Database locked (SQLite)?

```bash
# Stop all dotnet processes
Get-Process -Name dotnet | Stop-Process
dotnet run --project src/Web
```

### Migration errors in Docker?

```bash
# Clear volume and rebuild
docker compose down -v
docker compose up --build
```

### Port already in use?

Change in `src/Web/Properties/launchSettings.json`:

```json
{
  "applicationUrl": "http://localhost:5001"
}
```

